{{Quote|My Emperor, it is with great pleasure that I present the highlights of Order 66, compiled at the request of Imperial advisor Sate Pestage.|Casualty Report: Order 66|<ref name="Order 66: Destroy All Jedi">{{InsiderCite|87|Order 66: Destroy All Jedi}}</ref>}}
The '''casualty report of Order 66''' was compiled by the [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Imperial]] [[Moff/Legends|Moff]] [[Marcellin Wessel]]. It hailed [[Order 66/Legends|Order 66]] as a great Imperial success and went into detail about fifteen notable [[Jedi/Legends|Jedi]] victims of its execution. An image, a profile, and information about his or her termination were included for each Jedi. The official but untrue records of each termination were also supplemented by [[Sate Pestage/Legends|Sate Pestage]]. These records would later be revealed to the public in a cycle of [[Imperial HoloVision]].
{{Quote|Your Majesty: I have taken the liberty of appending the circumstances of death as they will appear in the official record. Please approve by 16:9:28 in time for the next cycle of Imperial Holovision|Sate Pestage|<ref name="Order 66: Destroy All Jedi" />}}
{{Quote|I trust that Your Majesty is pleased by the professionalism of the Empire's soldiers as evidenced by the thorough eradication of the Jedi rebellion. May your reign last for a thousand years!|Casualty Report: Order 66|<ref name="Order 66: Destroy All Jedi" />}}
The document was only available to [[Galactic Emperor/Legends|Emperor]] [[Palpatine/Legends|Palpatine]]. No others were to lay eyes on the report.

